    "game-id": "7232dfa78037a86047af82ad8c6bbbf4",
    "spell_type": "spell",
    "rank": 3,
    "text": "You create a dome of brilliant light that destroys projectiles attempting to pass through it. Ammunition from physical ranged attacks\u2014such as arrows, bolts, sling bullets, and other objects of similar size\u2014is destroyed in a flash of light when it passes into or out of the globe\u2019s area. Attackers targeting creatures or objects through the globe\u2019s surface with physical ranged attacks must succeed at a Fortitude save or become dazzled for 1 round (blinded for 1 round on a critical failure).",
